   453ŌåÆ/// to a more fully-featured serialization framework like `serde` or `sval`. A value visitor
   454ŌåÆ/// can differentiate primitive types through methods like [`VisitValue::visit_bool`] and
   455ŌåÆ/// [`VisitValue::visit_str`], but more complex types like maps and sequences
   456ŌåÆ/// will fallthrough to [`VisitValue::visit_any`].
